value:
One partner missing, the search is on.
Suddenly, a cry sounds from a hole!

Oh no! Now they're both in the hole!
"Together, we'll solve this in no time!"

One outstretched helping hand, and...
Back together, safe and sound!

Oh! It was a discovery! Of...jewels?!
A real diamond in the rough!

A faux summoning stone that radiates with
a summery, watermelon aura—but it can't
summon any Heroes. It's an event item.

Used in Aether Raids to build structures that
are available for a limited time. If that period
has elapsed, these stones will be lost.
